        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses changes in 5th edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> owing to new evidence. CD now places more value on action of external conditions; thinks lapse of time [required for development of species] not so great as some geologists have thought, and single variations [saltations] of even less importance compared with individual differences.</p> 
        </abstract>
